pose his travel order . In another he appeared to lash out at suggestions that Stephen K. Bannon his chief strategist holds the real power in the West Wing . A CNN poll released over the weekend said that 55 percent of Americans viewed Mr. Trump ’s travel order as an attempt to keep Muslims out of the country . The president also seemed angry about the story line
