d retroactively legalize Jewish settlements on privately owned Palestinian land . It was an assertive move by the right wing — but the law will likely be struck down by the country ’s high court . Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu was on his way back from a meeting with Britain ’s leaders as the law was being debated . _____ 6. Queen Elizabeth II ’s sapphire jubilee
